title: New fore fox browser
content:
I installed 'updated' product and it did not migrated the latest tool bars etc.....it downloaded material and tool bar from three+ years ago. Lost my pictures that showed up on computer when sleeping. Sites do not recognize this product anymore. Please help me....how do I get the old one back? Yes I am frustrated, sorry if I sound upset, just need some help....

Thank you, Al Sorestad
